data.eml:eml: The larvae of the European Helicopsyche species (Trichoptera: Helicopsychidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Waringer, Johann, Malicky, Hans, Živić, Ivana, Vicentini, Heinrich (2017): The larvae of the European Helicopsyche species (Trichoptera: Helicopsychidae). Zootaxa 4277 (4): 561-572, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4277.4.6
